'''地标塔81'''（{{lang-vi|The Landmark 81}}）是位於[[越南|越南]][[胡志明市|胡志明市]]的[[摩天大楼|摩天大楼]]，为全越南現時第一高的大厦（第二高是[[河内|河内]]的[[京南河内地标大厦|京南河内地标大厦]]，有72层），同時亦是全[[東南亞|東南亞]]目前[[东南亚摩天大楼列表|最高的摩天大楼]]。该摩天大楼由一家越南公司投资，由英国{{le|阿特金斯集团|Atkins (company)}}负责设计，前期筹备与设计进展多年，目前所有的设计工作已经基本定稿，总高461.2米，包括81层，总面积24万多平方米。投资金额尚不公布。2014年开始建设，于2018年开放，地标塔有三层高的商场、影院、会议室等。<ref name=autogeneral1>{{cite web|url=https://realestatevietnam.com.vn/the-tallest-building-in-vietnam-the-landmark-81-is-about-to-build-a-roof/|title=The Tallest Building In Vietnam – The Landmark 81 Is About To Build A Roof|publisher=realestatevietnam|accessdate=2018-03-29|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180329184250/https://realestatevietnam.com.vn/the-tallest-building-in-vietnam-the-landmark-81-is-about-to-build-a-roof/|archive-date=2018-03-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.atkinsglobal.com/en-gb/media-centre/news-releases/2015/aug/2015-08-03 |title=Atkins' architecture vision for Vingroup's tallest landmark building in Vietnam to become reality |accessdate=2018-03-29 |archive-date=2018-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180418034613/http://www.atkinsglobal.com/en-gb/media-centre/news-releases/2015/aug/2015-08-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

